name: Femi's Army: Now Let Us Pray
description:
God of the Almighty.
All of the Universe and Cosmos.
Earth Mother.
Ether Father.
Watch over this tribe.
May they walk light.
Fear less.
Understand and heed the word.
Whatever the outcome, know it is predestined.
It is written.
It is known.
Provide guidance through mind.
Honour, truth and respect.
And so be it.
And so it shall be.
